The seeker, undaunted, replied, "I am prepared to face whatever challenges come my way. I am prepared to unlock the secrets of the labyrinth."

The Keeper smiled, "Very well, then. To unlock the labyrinth, you must first prove yourself worthy. You must answer three riddles, each one more challenging than the last. If you answer correctly, the labyrinth shall be yours to explore. But if you fail, you shall never leave this place."

